From: Karya DE Team <karya@karya-de.org>
Date: Mon, 1 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 01] Karya Tiling - Custom tiling window manager for KWin

Adds auto-tiling support to KWin:
- Master-stack layout
- Split layout
- Grid layout
- Monocle layout
- Custom gap configuration
- Keyboard shortcuts: Meta+T toggle, Meta+Shift+T cycle layout

